\noindent{\bf Micro-averaging.}
With micro-averaging rather than macro-averages, 
the relative gains/losses across configs hardly change. The best results are
still with {\em amp}, reaching 84.7% recall and 24.9% AUC in Stage 1, and 44.7% R@P50 and 31.6% R@P80 in Stage 2.